The instances in this repository are sourced from the MIPLIB 2017 library and other public collections.

MIPLIB 2017
============
These instances are provided for scientific purposes. If you use MIPLIB 2017 instances in a publication, please cite the following paper:

Gleixner, A., Hendel, G., Gamrath, G. et al. The MIPLIB 2017, Collection and New Trends in Mixed-Integer Programming. Math. Prog. Comp. (2021). https://doi.org/10.1007/s12532-020-00194-3

Official Website: https://miplib.zib.de/

All other instance collections will have their own license and citation information in their respective subdirectories.
